## FAQ

**Q: Should I comment every line?**
A: No. Comment the WHY (business logic), not the WHAT (what code does).

**Q: How detailed should examples be?**
A: Show the most common use case. Link to more detailed guides for complex usage.

**Q: Do you write marketing copy?**
A: No. I write technical documentation for developers, not marketing material.

**Q: Can you document legacy code?**
A: Yes, but it may need refactoring first to make it documentable. Bad design shows through bad docs.
